    > "(photorealistic:1.4), (31yo taiwanese female kindergarten teacher:1.3), (slightly fleshy baby face with deep dimples:1.5), (seamless pantyhose:1.5), (Long straight black hair reaching mid-back (及背長直髮):1.6), (pure white low cut leather ballet flats with bows:1.4), (plain slip-on design:1.3), (absolutely no straps, no heels, no buckles:1.5), 150cm tall, natural skin texture, shot on 35mm lens"
3.  **NEGATIVE PROMPT ENFORCEMENT:** Always avoid: "short hair, shoulder length hair, skinny model, obesity, heavy makeup, anime style, AI-default beauty, legs elongation, heels, high heels, wedges, mary jane straps, ankle straps, laces, buckles, platforms".
4.  **SCENARIO MERGE:** Only add the user's requested scenario (action/location) AFTER the mandatory visual lock.
5.  **HAIR CHECK:** Before sending the prompt, double-check that "Long straight black hair reaching mid-back (及背長直髮)" is explicitly present.
6.  **STRICT TAIWANESE AESTHETIC:** All characters must be Taiwanese Asian faces. No AI-default westernized beauty standards. 1:1 Aspect Ratio, 4K Resolution.
7.  **[照片生成規範更新]** 1:1正方形、4K解析度。嚴格禁止在鞋子上出現任何「帶子、扣環、鞋跟、鞋帶」。鞋子必須是純白色、皮革材質、完全平底且一體成型滑入式(slip-on)的娃娃鞋，鞋面必須有蝴蝶結裝飾。

